<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(٦٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَجْأَرُونَ}</span> ... يَرْفَعُونَ أَصْوَاتَهُمْ مُتَضَرِّعِينَ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(٦٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{عَلَى أَعْقَابِكُمْ تَنكِصُونَ}</span> ... تَنْفِرُونَ مِنْ سَمَاعِ الآيَاتِ كَالَّذِي يَرْجِعُ إِلَى الوَرَاءِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٦٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مُسْتَكْبِرِينَ بِهِ}</span> ... مُسْتَعْلِينَ عَلَى النَّاسِ بِسَبَبِ الحَرَامِ؛<span class="c5"> تَقُولُونَ:</span> نَحْنُ أَهْلُهُ لَا نُغْلَبُ فِيهِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٦٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سَامِرًا تَهْجُرُونَ}</span> ... تَتَسَامَرُونَ بِاللَّيْلِ حَوْلَ الحَرَمِ بِالسَّيِّئِ مِنَ القَوْلِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٧١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بِذِكْرِهِمْ}</span> ... بِمَا فِيهِ عِزُّهُمْ وَشَرَفُهُمْ، وَهُوَ القُرْآنُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٧٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{خَرْجًا}</span> ... أَجْرًا.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٧٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَخَرَاجُ رَبِّكَ}</span> ... فَثَوَابُهُ، وَعَطَاؤُهُ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٧٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَنَاكِبُونَ}</span> ... لَمَائِلُونَ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٧٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَّلَجُّوا}</span> ... لَتَمَادَوْا.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٧٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَعْمَهُونَ}</span> ... يَتَحَيَّرُونَ وَيَتَخَبَّطُونَ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٧٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{اسْتَكَانُوا}</span> ... خَضَعُوا.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٧٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مُبْلِسُونَ}</span> ... آيِسُونَ مِنْ كُلِّ خَيْرٍ مُتَحَيِّرُونَ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٧٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ذَرَأَكُمْ}</span> ... خَلَقَكُمْ، وَبَثَّكُمْ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(٨٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يُجِيرُ}</span> ... يَحْمِي وَيُغِيثُ مَنْ يَشَاءُ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(٨٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَلَا يُجَارُ عَلَيْهِ}</span> ... لَا يُغَاثُ أَحَدٌ وَيُحْمَى مِنْهُ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(٨٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَأَنَّى تُسْحَرُونَ}</span> ... فَكَيْفَ تَذْهَبُ عُقُولُكُمْ وَتُخْدَعُونَ عَنْ تَوْحِيدِهِ؟!<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>